{"tid":1326150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我以後唔會再亂屌人廢老","createTime":"2019-07-17T06:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T08:44:14.000Z","uid":212927,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"84469df6db610b73bc0c53080ced32e58ad987e0","tid":1326150,"uid":212927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"真人真事<br />\n啱啱落百佳買嘢俾錢嗰陣<br />\n有個望落去六十幾歲嘅姨姨收銀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=收銀員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:有冇出去遊行啊細佬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:有啊(以為佢會屌鳩我出去搞事)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:加油啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(勁感動)<br />\n<br />\n雖然只係好行嘅三個字，但由一個陌生人親口同我講就成個感覺唔同晒，我以後一定唔會亂屌人廢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721一定要出黎發夢，加油啊香港人！</span>"},{"pid":"53c2eead8acb5aa3d21e359d69a6c9387d7774ce","tid":1326150,"uid":232229,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"近呢個月發覺其實好多老人家都好明白事理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc4b67517e5738fd8d7c7e78d49b2decb5b6ee0","tid":1326150,"uid":147047,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:18:04.000Z","msg":"雨革已經俾人分化左<br />\n<br />\n以為後生先會示威"},{"pid":"42c438c3a416aa451e480e0129e3f788986cb570","tid":1326150,"uid":200900,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"寫連儂牆嗰陣好多打工仔同我講加油 小心d<br />\n雖然只係簡單幾嗰字<br />\n但係由陌生嘅中年人講就覺得香港有救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198463a2163d39339fb14f156aac5e0e1a89df94","tid":1326150,"uid":143151,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"琴日 係連儂牆有個伯伯問我點寫字<br />\n好撚感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有次發完夢 食薩莉亞<br />\n落單個呀姨 譚仔口音 <br />\n但同我哋講 靠哂你哋班年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02ff8547305c3df5fda3574a529011346d26de5","tid":1326150,"uid":121286,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"我會分支持既叫伯伯婆婆，藍既就叫番廢老"},{"pid":"423122fd4a96a1b46ba814ff88b0077b4d4afc48","tid":1326150,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"屌廢老之前聽下佢地講乜先啦<br />\n唔係老D的人就一定係廢老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeca59c40e62b4e9bd1d57e152ecc63b5f153f16","tid":1326150,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"好感動但唔好亂認去過發夢呀"},{"pid":"4fee09c68109d5aabccecb481bd325f57c7d946f","tid":1326150,"uid":278765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"頭腦思想是否進化，舆年紀冇關。貼大埔連儂牆時，就見到好幾個嬸嬙在貼，佢地嘅訊息，基本上同我嘅差唔多！都係和理非系列的 😄"},{"pid":"2775e86105f063886a5ea04e47f77708ee2e0ea4","tid":1326150,"uid":54121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aeca59c40e62b4e9bd1d57e152ecc63b5f153f16","tid":1326150,"uid":169495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"好感動但唔好亂認去過發夢呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"佢問樓主有冇去遊行啫<br />\n如果真係問有冇去衝梗係唔好理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f19b83ed3d6c457a72d2fe452b08a97c7b222ef","tid":1326